      "title": "[正面] A \"roguelite\" deckbuilder with gacha in it. Artsty...",
      "summary": "A \"roguelite\" deckbuilder with gacha in it. Artstyle is nice, the story is compelling, and I like the vibe. It kinda reminds me of arknights a lil'. Characters have voice overs which is a nice bonus. And as mentioned by others, the translation is abit wonky as it's MTL. Usually, MTL is fine as it provides some comical relief, but during serious moments of the story, it kinda brings the vibe down.\r\n\r\nFor the gacha elements, I think it's a bonus as the game provides enough for you to have fun with. Starting units are good, and it really depends on how well you utilize them. They also give a ton of stuff starting out. So, pretty much F2P friendly. Game mechanics is also nice to play with, and has managed to hold my attention for more than an hour... which means a pretty good start for the game.",
